# megadev.ai Project Context

## Vision

Building a personal career persona website that represents the "megadev" identity - someone who leverages hyper-leverage tools and skills in the age of guilds. Tools best used by the creator, available to all.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Vite + React + TypeScript
- **Styling**: CSS with CSS variables (no Tailwind unless added)
- **Deployment**: Static export to Hostinger
- **No backend**: Pure frontend, static files only

## Design Aesthetic

- **Theme**: Blueprint/technical schematic
- **Background**: Cobalt blue `#0047AB`
- **Accent**: Cyan glow `#00D4FF`
- **Character**: Modified Zero from Mega Man (blue, no hair)
- **Layout**: Single viewport, no scrolling

## Key Interactive Element

The **whip** weapon represents the [claiw](https://github.com/sungchun12/claiw) CLI AI tool:
- Hover: Cyan glow effect
- Click: Opens GitHub repo in new tab

